noteType=12
noteToRead="I had Jerry over here
despite my mother's wishes.
He brings me comfort, but
I have this nagging thought
that it won't last.
I should enjoy this
while it's here.

My mother came home
earlier than I thought.
She can't catch me here
with him. We hid
in the utility closet
till the coast was clear.

          -Claire"

if global.gateHProg>=27 {instance_destroy()}
